These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: peas, cherry
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, mystery
1. the person watching animation movies is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
2. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | iced-tea      |
| Food          | cherry | peas    |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | mystery      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, musician
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane
1. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
3. the musician is not to the right of the doctor##8
4. the person driving the skateboard is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | 7up        | milk    |
| Hobby       | gardening         | skydiving |
| Job         | musician | doctor   |
| Transport   | skateboard               | airplane  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, horror
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, techno
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, indonesian
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse
1. the thai is in an odd position##4
2. the indonesian is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | family       | horror |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | techno    |
| Nationality   | thai | indonesian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig        | horse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
