The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike
1. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the writer##5
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | cooking  |
| Job           | writer  | electrician |
| Nationality   | british | chinese   |
| Transport     | quad-bike   | boat |

