2. the person driving the taxi is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
4. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8
5. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person eating plum##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
